We also offer branded shoes repair like Birkenstocks repair, Birkenstock sandal repair etc. Along with repair services, we also provide extensive varieties of fantastic Berkeley shoes, totes, belts and different items on our local and online store. We are leading shoe store in Berkeley and were voted “Best of the East Bay”. Our 40 years of experience will stand you in good stead whether you’re bringing in combat boots, stilettos or Birkenstocks. We are good and healthy choice when it comes to find shoe stores in Berkeley. For people looking for shoes in Berkeley CA we work along with local doctors and podiatrists therefore you will find products that will benefit foot care needs.
